manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "user"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "user"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.69"
async-graphql = "5.0.6"
async-graphql-axum = "5.0.6"
axum = "0.6.9"
mongodb = "2.3.1"
thiserror = "1.0.38"
tracing = "0.1.37"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.152"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.25.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.validator]
version = "0.16.0"
